{"tid":1512080,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"( #Metoo集會 )  我有野想講，希望大家留意危險人物","createTime":"2019-08-27T17:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T07:18:29.000Z","uid":94499,"like":57,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"eb017f05c5ab65d96a9e8a4ac26da21f44accc33","tid":1512080,"uid":94499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:36:57.000Z","msg":"今次集會，<br />\n最重要聲援男女義士受到黑警性暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n此外，大家都好記得何式凝呢條友出賣天水圍前線，<br />\n事後仲出post扮到好無辜，推哂責任咁⋯⋯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8O9sobO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8O9sobO.jpg&h=1b48b43d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有一個，都想大家要留意叫「黎明」呢個女學者，<br />\n佢不停利用metoo去拎政治光環<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e2GuBwY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe2GuBwY.jpg&h=b58f3c5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OPiHWwY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOPiHWwY.jpg&h=170ab55d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢係上海人，係有共產背景<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未知今次8.28集會有無佢份，怕佢今次又拎光環<br />\n亦聽聞佢嚟近有選舉，好怕有受傷男女義士名單交到佢手上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個唔該就送上中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家留意今次集會既嘉賓有無呢個人</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qeXBgz0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqeXBgz0.jpg&h=562a0645&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d1d7a736540e13640c10be8148b1e23bcc4aef2","tid":1512080,"uid":94499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" 